{
  "stem": "10406.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, we knew something was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was-- it started like Monday morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It probably started before that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The way they operated, they probably surrounded the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was already surrounded, and you couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so this was the starting point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- we lasted there a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was one woman there that had maybe five or six children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one little girl, the youngest, was a few years old, was crying a lot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was, of course, that was dangerous because they'll catch everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the mother decided to take that little girl out and put her to sleep up in-- in-- in the room on top in a bed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the little girl woke up, or somebody woke her up, there was a Ukrainian policeman there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she-- the little girl was crying, mama, mama.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was saying to her, you know, where-- like she was leading him to-- to the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she remembered the entrance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The entrance there was through to-- to a toilet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so she was leading him in that direction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was-- It was underneath the toilet?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was an opening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like it was designed so that it could be moved away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was underneath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this policemen, you know, he-- he knew where she was leading him, but he couldn't find any connection, any opening, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it took, I think, more than an hour or two before they finally-- because this little girl went away and she kept coming back to that same area.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got suspicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew there was a hiding place there already, because the girl was going there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually, they-- they moved that whole assembly.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
